le is 3.5x larger\nthan the current SDSS sample of similar galaxies, thereby providing a new path\nforward for transient science and galaxy evolution studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Oct 2018 19:00:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-29"}
